# interview service

Module: `github.com/sedorofeevd/project-druzya/services/interview`. Work from service root only.

## Layers

```
cmd/interview/app/run.go       → DI
internal/app/api/interview/    → gRPC/HTTP (one RPC per file)
internal/interview/            → model, repository, service
internal/adapter/content/      → content-service gRPC client
internal/adapter/events/       → EventPublisher
```

HTTP `:8082`, gRPC `:9092`. See `AGENTS.md`.
